WEBVTT
NOTE OE3D — Script5 — English

1
00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:01.484
Hello!

2
00:00:01.434 --> 00:00:06.059
You have just received your new orthosis at our practice, Ortho Espace 3D.

3
00:00:06.059 --> 00:00:09.439
The first days are an important adaptation period.

4
00:00:09.439 --> 00:00:12.034
Here are our tips to get started well.

5
00:00:13.434 --> 00:00:15.058
Fitting the orthosis.

6
00:00:15.008 --> 00:00:18.451
First put on a thin stocking or sock without thick seams.

7
00:00:18.451 --> 00:00:22.709
Then position the orthosis according to the markers shown by your practitioner.

8
00:00:22.709 --> 00:00:25.889
Fasten the straps from bottom to top, without overtightening.

9
00:00:27.289 --> 00:00:29.178
Building up wear time.

10
00:00:29.128 --> 00:00:32.115
In the first days, limit wearing to two hours.

11
00:00:32.115 --> 00:00:35.064
Increase gradually according to your tolerance.

12
00:00:35.064 --> 00:00:39.435
If you feel discomfort or pain, remove the orthosis and contact us.

13
00:00:40.835 --> 00:00:42.526
The condition of your skin.

14
00:00:42.476 --> 00:00:46.756
After each wear, carefully inspect the skin in contact with the orthosis.

15
00:00:46.756 --> 00:00:50.036
A slight redness that disappears in twenty minutes is normal.

16
00:00:50.036 --> 00:00:54.803
However, persistent redness or a wound requires immediate consultation.

17
00:00:56.203 --> 00:00:58.007
Daily use.

18
00:00:57.957 --> 00:01:02.936
Wear your orthosis for all your usual activities, gradually increasing the level of effort.

19
00:01:02.936 --> 00:01:08.031
Physical therapy will help you regain independence and comfort in all your daily movements.

20
00:01:09.431 --> 00:01:12.739
Our team is available to answer all your questions.

21
00:01:12.689 --> 00:01:16.441
Do not hesitate to call us or send us a message on WhatsApp.

22
00:01:16.441 --> 00:01:18.717
Courage — you are not alone!
